OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776787870
OL,3,CStarmer urged to include appointment
OL,4,Cof former Police Ombudsman in vetting
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FThe DUP Leader has asked the Prime
OL,8,FMinister to include the appointment of
OL,9,Fthe former Police Ombudsman for
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland, Marie Anderson, in a
OL,11,Freview of security vetting procedures
OL,12,Fin the wake of the Lord Mandelson
OL,13,Faffair.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776787870
OL,3,CStarmer urged to include appointment
OL,4,Cof former Police Ombudsman in vetting
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FSpeaking in the House of Commons,
OL,8,FGavin Robinson said: "The Prime
OL,9,FMinister knows that he is the main
OL,10,Fcharacter in an ongoing national
OL,11,Fscandal, and given all the blame
OL,12,Fapportioned in his statement, it is
OL,13,Fincredible that only one person has
OL,14,Flost their position.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776787870
OL,3,CStarmer urged to include appointment
OL,4,Cof former Police Ombudsman in vetting
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,F"But would the Prime Minister also
OL,8,Frecognize it is incredible to learn
OL,9,Fthat in Northern Ireland, a political
OL,10,Fappointment was made. Following the
OL,11,Frefusal to clear an individual for
OL,12,Fsecurity access, that they have
OL,13,Fcontinued in their post, engaged on
OL,14,Fissues connected with the legacy of
OL,15,Four troubled past with full security
OL,16,Fclearance, despite security service
OL,17,Fconcerns and they continue to this day.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776787870
OL,3,CStarmer urged to include appointment
OL,4,Cof former Police Ombudsman in vetting
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,F"So if the Prime Minister's ordering a
OL,8,Freview by Sir Adrian Fulford, will he
OL,9,Fensure it includes within its terms of
OL,10,Freference or separately, a deep dive
OL,11,Finto the appointment of Marie
OL,12,FAnderson, the Northern Ireland Police
OL,13,FOmbudsman - why she was appointed, why
OL,14,Fthe security information was ignored,
OL,15,Fand how this can be the case."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776787870
OL,3,CStarmer urged to include appointment
OL,4,Cof former Police Ombudsman in vetting
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FMarie Anderson took up the position of
OL,8,FPolice Ombudsman for Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fin 2019 and, after a leave of absence
OL,10,Flast year, retired on 31 December
OL,11,F2025. Recruitment for her successor is
OL,12,Fnow underway.
OL,14,FA Northern Ireland Office spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid:
OL,17,F"Marie Anderson was appointed in 2019
OL,18,Fby the then Secretary of State.
OL,19,FFollowing concerns raised today, we
OL,20,Fare looking into our records and will
OL,21,Frespond as soon as possible.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,449,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1776787870
OL,3,CStarmer urged to include appointment
OL,4,Cof former Police Ombudsman in vetting
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,F"The Prime Minister has also confirmed
OL,8,Fthis matter will be included as part
OL,9,Fof the Fulford review."
OL,11,FUTV has approached Ms Anderson, the
OL,12,FPolice Ombudsman for Northern Ireland,
OL,13,Fand the Department of Justice for
OL,14,Fcomment.
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
